# Plan: Add `packages/generator-rest-client`

## Context

The goal is to add a new Prisma generator package `@prisma/generator-rest-client` that reads the DMMF (Data Model Meta Format) from a Prisma schema and emits a single `rest-client.ts` file containing:
- Typed TypeScript interfaces for every model and its CRUD input types
- A `RestClient` class whose properties are per-model objects with `findMany`, `findUnique`, `create`, `update`, and `delete` methods that call HTTP endpoints

The generator integrates with the Prisma generator protocol via `generatorHandler` from `@prisma/generator-helper`, which handles JSON-RPC 2.0 communication over stdin/stderr. It is a standalone process-based generator, so the compiled output needs a `#!/usr/bin/env node` shebang and a `bin` declaration to be invocable as `prisma-generator-rest-client`.

---

## Critical files to read (already read and understood)

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `packages/generator-helper/src/generatorHandler.ts` | JSON-RPC handler — the `Handler` interface and `generatorHandler` function |
| `packages/generator/src/configuration.ts` | `GeneratorManifest`, `GeneratorOptions`, `GeneratorConfig`, `EnvValue` types |
| `packages/dmmf/src/dmmf.ts` | DMMF types: `Document`, `Model`, `Field`, `FieldKind` |
| `packages/internals/src/utils/parseEnvValue.ts` | `parseEnvValue(EnvValue): string` — resolves env-var references in output paths |
| `packages/credentials-store/helpers/build.ts` | Canonical `helpers/build.ts` pattern: `void build(adapterConfig)` |
| `helpers/compile/configs.ts` | `adapterConfig`, `createAdapterConfig` — CJS+ESM bundled build helpers |
| `helpers/compile/build.ts` | `BuildOptions` type (extends `esbuild.BuildOptions`), includes `banner` support |
| `tsconfig.build.bundle.json` | Paths map — must add new package entry here |

---

## Files to create

### 1. `packages/generator-rest-client/package.json`

```json
{
  "name": "@prisma/generator-rest-client",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "description": "This package is intended for Prisma's internal use",
  "main": "dist/index.js",
  "module": "dist/index.mjs",
  "types": "dist/index.d.ts",
  "bin": {
    "prisma-generator-rest-client": "./dist/index.js"
  },
  "exports": {
    ".": {
      "require": {
        "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
        "default": "./dist/index.js"
      },
      "import": {
        "types": "./dist/index.d.mts",
        "default": "./dist/index.mjs"
      }
    }
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/prisma/prisma.git",
    "directory": "packages/generator-rest-client"
  },
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "dependencies": {
    "@prisma/dmmf": "workspace:*",
    "@prisma/generator": "workspace:*",
    "@prisma/generator-helper": "workspace:*",
    "@prisma/internals": "workspace:*",
    "fs-extra": "11.3.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/fs-extra": "11.0.4",
    "@types/node": "~20.19.24"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "DEV=true tsx helpers/build.ts",
    "build": "tsx helpers/build.ts",
    "prepublishOnly": "pnpm run build",
    "test": "vitest run"
  },
